# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  AUTH
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. LOGIN — obtiene access_token + refresh_token
POST {{base}}/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_user": "SuperAdmin",
  "password": "supersegura123"
}



### Audit Log
GET {{base}}/audit-log HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Nómina Preview
GET {{base}}/nomina/preview?id_empleado=149&id_ubicacion=65&fecha_inicio=2026-05-01&fecha_fin=2026-05-14 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Empleados por servicio
GET {{base}}/nomina/empleados-zona?id_zona=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


###
GET {{base}}/dashboard/resumen
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 
GET {{base}}/dashboard/zona/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 2. ME — datos del usuario logueado
GET {{base}}/auth/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. REFRESH TOKEN — renueva access_token
POST {{base}}/auth/refresh HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{refresh}}

###

### 4. LOGOUT — cierra sesión actual
POST {{base}}/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refresh}}"
}

###

### 5. LOGOUT ALL — cierra todas las sesiones
POST {{base}}/auth/logout-all HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. REGISTRO usuario (solo admin o superior)
POST {{base}}/auth/registro HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan",
  "paterno": "Pérez",
  "materno": "García",
  "name_user": "j.perez.g",
  "correo": "juan.perez@empresa.com",
  "password": "Segura123!",
  "id_rol_sistema": 3,
  "id_empresa_default": 1
}

###

### 7. BIOMÉTRICO — buscar guardia (requiere X-API-KEY)
POST {{base}}/auth/biometrico/buscar HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: {{apikey}}

{
  "query": "LODR951031FF3"
}

###

### 8. BIOMÉTRICO — login (requiere X-API-KEY)
POST {{base}}/auth/biometrico/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: {{apikey}}

{
  "id": 178,
  "biometrico_token": "178-1746123456"
}



