Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. LISTAR con filtros
GET {{base}}/empleados?pagina=1&limit=20&status=1&fechas=2025-01-01 a 2025-12-31 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. DETALLE de un empleado
GET {{base}}/empleados/177 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 12. BUSCAR empleados
GET {{base}}/empleados/buscar?search=juan&limit=20&offset=0 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. DASHBOARD conteos
GET {{base}}/empleados/dashboard HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 14. ALERTAS (incidencias pendientes + perfiles incompletos)
GET {{base}}/empleados/alertas HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

